DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-378. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Haas.

Upon consideration of respondent’s motion to supplement record,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to supplement record be, and hereby is, granted, and respondent shall file the supplemental documents within seven days of the date of this entry.

Douglas and Resnick, JJ., dissent. Lundberg Stratton, J., not participating.
